## ğŸ“œ Running Tests

### **1ï¸âƒ£ Run All Tests**
```sh
npx playwright test
```

### **2ï¸âƒ£ Run Tests for Web Applications Only**
```sh
npx playwright test tests/webApp.spec.ts
```

### **3ï¸âƒ£ Run Tests for Mobile Applications Only**
```sh
npx playwright test tests/mobileApp.spec.ts
```

### **4ï¸âƒ£ Run a Single Test**
```sh
npx playwright test -g "Verify 'Implement user authentication'"
```

