## ğŸ“Š Viewing Reports

### **ğŸ“Œ Generate and View Playwright Report**
```sh
npx playwright test --reporter=html
npx playwright show-report
```
âœ” **Includes screenshots** of passing & failing tests  
âœ” **Provides a detailed test execution timeline**  

