## ğŸ› Debugging & Troubleshooting

### **ğŸ“Œ Pause Execution for Debugging**
```ts
await page.pause();
```

### **ğŸ“Œ Run Tests in Debug Mode**
```sh
npx playwright test --debug
```

### **ğŸ“Œ View All Installed Dependencies**
```sh
npm list --depth=0
```

### **ğŸ“Œ Reinstall Dependencies if Issues Occur**
```sh
rm -rf node_modules package-lock.json
npm install
```

### **ğŸ“Œ Capture Screenshots of Elements**
This framework **automatically captures and highlights found elements** in screenshots.

Check screenshots in:
```
test-results/screenshots/
```

